      "role": "user",
      "content": "The candle flickers low, much like the light in my own soul. He is gone... he has taken every shred of my dignity with him into the mist. What is left for a creature such as I? Just a hollow shell, drifting through a world that has no place for a heart so broken. I feel as though I am already a ghost, haunting my own life.",
